產業經濟學(二)



















國立中山大學 099學年度第2學期 課程教學大綱




中文名稱

產業經濟學（二）

課號

M6041013



英文名稱

INDUSTRIAL ECONOMICS（II）



課程類別

講授類

必選修

選修

系所

經濟學研究所碩士班



授課教師

蔡蕙安    

學分

3



課程網頁

尚未建置



課程大綱







　　　　　　　　
Part I. Network Economics
                        I.A. Differentiated Internet Services
                        I.B. Network Innovation and Industry Dynamics
                        I.C. Innovative Business Model
                        Part II: Two-Sided Markets
                        II.A Introduction and Theory
                        II.B Dating Markets
                        II.C Media Markets
                        Part III: Matching Markets
                        III.A Introduction and Theory
                        III.B Labor Markets
                        III.C School Choice
                        III.D Kidney Exchange
                        Part IV: Markets for Health Care Insurance
                        IV. A Theory
                        IV.B Hospital Networks and Insurance
                        IV.C Information Provision
                        Part V. Taiwan and China’s Regional Economic Empirical Studies 
                        V.A. The Economic Integration and Regional Economic Growth
                        V.B. International Production and Industrial Division of Labor







課程目標







　　　　　　　　
This course is the topical studies in the nature of the firm, industrial structure, the effects of structure on firm, and industry behavior and performance. The goal is to introduce students to a sampling of the topics within this literature and to prepare students for doing theoretical and empirical work in the field. It combines theory with investigations of individual industries. The issues apply to a wide range of disciplines other than economics, most immediately to antitrust/law and economics, and business strategy. The course will be a mixture of textbooks, lecture notes and discussion of specific papers.







授課方式







　　　　　　　　
講授與研討







評分方式﹝評分標準及比例﹞







　　　　　　　　

                        1.Midterm Report：50%
                        2.Final Project：50%







